r\">PR</a> 在 主题仓库的 <code v-pre>/theme/src/node/locales</code> 目录中按照相同的方式添加语言。</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"为每个语言设置主题选项\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#为每个语言设置主题选项\"><span>为每个语言设置主题选项</span></a></h2>\n<p>与站点配置和 <code v-pre>@vuepress/theme-default</code> 的主题配置相同，<code v-pre>vuepress-theme-plume</code> 也支持你在主题选项中设置 locale 选项，并为每种语言设置不同的配置。</p>\n<CodeTabs id=\"60\" :data='[{\"id\":\".vuepress/config.ts\"}]'><template #title0=\"{ value, isActive }\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-typescript\"/><span>.vuepress/config.ts</span></template><template #tab0=\"{ value, isActive }\"><div class=\"language-ts\" data-ext=\"ts\" data-title=\"ts\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">import</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> {</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> defineUserConfig</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> }</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> from</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> '</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">vuepress</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">import</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> {</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> plumeTheme</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> }</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> from</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> '</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">vuepress-theme-plume</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shik